android.permission.REORDER_TASKS.description: Allows an application to move tasks to the foreground and background. Malicious applications can force themselves to the front without your control.

playstore_details.title: Muscle Monster Workout Planner
playstore_details.description:
The Ultimate AI-Driven Workout App for Faster, Smarter Results: 
Achieve your fitness goals with the Muscle Monster Workout Planner! Whether you’re looking to lose weight, build muscle, or enhance your strength, this workout program is your ultimate guide. Perfect for men dedicated to muscle building, this workout planner app helps you sculpt your dream physique and reach new levels of performance. Unlock your full potential and become a true calisthenics monster!

Experience the Following Benefits:
- A personalized workout planner right in your pocket
- Master 300+ fitness moves for precise targeting of your body's key areas
- 21 Day workout free challenge
- Availability of a variety of calisthenics exercises and routines
- Get a stronger and more flexible body
- Personalized AI Trainer
- Immersive fitness instruction
- You can practice anytime, anywhere

Muscle Monster is your virtual personal trainer, guiding you through a variety of calisthenics exercises and routines, all tailored to your fitness level and goals. Whether you are a beginner or an advanced calisthenics practitioner, this app has got you covered.

The Ultimate Male Fitness App for Calisthenics Enthusiasts. With Muscle Monster, you can unlock a whole new realm of calisthenics training, right at your fingertips.

[ 0 Basic Muscle Apps: Start from basic ]
No matter what your fitness level is, our muscle fitness app is your go-to solution for all your workout needs. Whether you're a fitness enthusiast or a calisthenics beginner, this Workout Planner app makes it easy for you to start your fitness journey with or without equipment.

[ Workout Planner: 21 Day Workout Challenge Free ]
Say goodbye to generic workout routines. Participate in the 21 Day Workout Challenge for free. Our app is equipped with cutting-edge AI technology that tailors your workout planner free to match your specific goals, whether it's weight loss, muscle gain, or a combination of both.

[ Start Training Workout Planner With One Click ]
No more complicated setups or confusing workouts. Just select your preferred workout time, click "Start," and dive into a world of fitness enjoyment immediately. Gain muscle, calisthenics lose weight, or just keep fit - Muscle Monster provides a personalized daily workout plan that exactly fits your goals and lifestyle.

[ Fitness Trend Review ]
Track your fitness journey with ease. Our app keeps detailed records of your workouts, helping you witness the incredible power of consistency as you make progress toward your goals.

Muscle Monster Workout Planner - Best Muscle Booster App for men
What do you need to share?
- Define your fitness goal: Calisthenics Weight loss, muscle gain, or both.
- Share your physical details: Age, height, and weight.
- Tell us about your daily routine: Your activity level, posture concerns, and more.

Pro tip: Be honest in your answers, and you'll receive a fitness plan tailored to your unique needs.

With these elements, we craft a personalized 21-day workout plan designed to help you achieve visible changes in your body. Our extensive exercise library includes a variety of workouts for different goals – whether you're targeting specific muscle groups, aiming for weight loss, or muscle gain, we've got you covered. We meticulously track your daily progress, record fitness data, and celebrate your commitment to the journey.

You'll have access to a library of 200+ workouts, including:
- Gym & home workout planner
- 21-day workout challenge
- Fitness trainer
- Muscle strengthening exercises
- Home workout
- Muscle gain or weight-loss workouts
- Gym or at-home routines with minimum or no equipment at all
- Calisthenics or dumbbell home workouts.

Don’t miss out! Explore our upcoming fitness events and special offers to supercharge your workout routine. Join the Muscle Monster Workout Planner today and transform your body easily. Your health, wellness, and fitness goals are just a click away.

high.title: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
high.description:
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.

hotspot.title: Found 8 critical permission(s)
hotspot.description:
Ensure that these permissions are required by the application.

android.permission.READ_MEDIA_IMAGES (dangerous): allows reading image files from external storage. - Allows an application to read image files from external storage.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE (dangerous): read external storage contents - Allows an application to read from external storage.

android.permission.CAMERA (dangerous): take pictures and videos - Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.GET_TASKS (dangerous): retrieve running applications - Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.READ_CALENDAR (dangerous): read calendar events - Allows an application to read all of the calendar events stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your calendar events to other people.

android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR (dangerous): add or modify calendar events and send emails to guests - Allows an application to add or change the events on your calendar, which may send emails to guests. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your calendar events or to send emails to guests.

android.permission.POST_NOTIFICATIONS (dangerous): allows an app to post notifications. - Allows an app to post notifications

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE (dangerous): read phone state and identity - Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.
